sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant C as Cartograph
    participant R as Retrieval
    participant A as Agent

    U->>C: Describe issue
    C->>R: Find relevant files
    R-->>C: Files + graph context
    C-->>U: Shows context panel
    U->>C: Click Fix This
    C->>A: Spawn with context
    A-->>C: Stream progress
    C-->>U: Show diff
    U->>C: Approve
    C->>A: Create PR
